rows.label: fev02_360_125_msg0001
rows.name: Looks like this is the way to the hangar.

rows.label: fev02_360_125_msg0002
rows.name: Sounds like a way out of here!

rows.label: fev02_360_125_msg0003
rows.name:
Meh-meh-meh...
Door is locked, no way to open!

rows.label: fev02_360_125_msg0004
rows.name:
Even Hana probably not able to
break through this...

rows.label: fev02_360_125_msg0006
rows.name: Rex. Take a look over there.

rows.label: fev02_360_125_msg0007
rows.name:
Good eyes. Could that be the
switch to open it?

rows.label: fev02_360_125_msg0008
rows.name:
We don't have many options
but to try.

rows.label: fev02_360_125_msg0009
rows.name:
If it does open the door, we will surely
be able to escape through the hangar.

rows.label: fev02_360_125_msg0010
rows.name: Then what are we waiting for?!

rows.label: fev02_360_125_msg0011
rows.name:
Looks like we have to leave this room
for now and find a way up there.
